opendial.bn.values

Class RelationalVal

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.datastructs.Graph<Value,java.lang.String>
      • opendial.bn.values.RelationalVal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Value>, Value

    public class RelationalVal
extends Graph<Value,java.lang.String>
implements Value
    Representation of a relational value. Its extends a graph where the nodes contains Value objects, and the relation are plain strings. See the Graph class for more information about the syntax for the graph.
